# AutoCAD-BlockBox .gitignore
# Purpose: Keep development files clean while allowing source DWG blocks,
# package definitions, changelogs, documentation, and release metadata to be tracked.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Windows / Dropbox / System Noise
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
*.tmp
*.temp
~$*

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# AutoCAD Temporary / Lock / Backup Files
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.bak
*.sv$
*.ac$
*.dwl
*.dwl2
*.log
*.err

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# AutoCAD Plot / Publish Output
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.plt
*.pc3.bak
*.pdf.bak

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local Scratch / Testing Folders
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
_temp/
temp/
scratch/
testing/
_local/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Optional Export Output
# Keep source DWGs tracked, but ignore temporary export work areas.
# Remove these lines if you decide to version exported static block packages.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/export/temp/
**/export/_working/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Release ZIP Handling
# Current recommendation: DO NOT ignore release ZIPs by default.
# BlockBox release ZIPs may be tracked or uploaded to GitHub Releases.
# Uncomment these only if you want Git to ignore generated ZIP files.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# releases/current/*.zip
# releases/archive/*.zip
# *.zip

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Keep Folder Placeholders
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
!.gitkeep
